{"tid":2125271,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"e+應該製造輿論 救埋HA想清算嘅醫護手足","createTime":"2020-07-26T05:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T09:15:39.000Z","uid":123774,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d521e5419a9cf7167571bd68b6457fb134d54db6","tid":2125271,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:29:08.000Z","msg":"話說林鄭醫管局見疫情減退<br />\n以為罷工醫護已經無利用價值<br />\nHA六月請律師想清算醫護<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5C9CMT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5C9CMT.png&h=95cb3e72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當初醫護罷工係要求政府抗疫對症下藥<br />\n而唔係反政府<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0biv7r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0biv7r.jpg&h=965a096b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果各方壓力下林鄭先半封關<br />\n事後證明第二波全部都係輸入<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>第三波爆發係錯誤邊境措施引發<br />\n正正證明當初醫護有先見之明</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n爆發三個禮拜死咗八九個人<br />\n零售業同經濟百業蕭條 失業率創新高<br />\n呢啲全部都係因為政府唔聽專業勸喻嘅結果<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>醫護要留響前線同病毒搏鬥<br />\n放工又怕感染屋企 <br />\n住酒店又被歧視<br />\n仲要不時面對支共/民建聯威脅搵支那醫護黎<br />\n<br />\n所以醫護唔應該再面對清算</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"524b6655249aece0165bad8d6b5f8102c6e482e1","tid":2125271,"uid":162954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:30:20.000Z","msg":"迫仆街政府跪低"},{"pid":"b343ca90ef6467563d121bd3cd6600ff2cd8594a","tid":2125271,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:34:56.000Z","msg":"幫手留icon推下"},{"pid":"2e9bab5fa2b7171e4118ef09297389f8ea5f519b","tid":2125271,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c10b3a7b29ff538ac77b0637e4362c9b905badb","tid":2125271,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b343ca90ef6467563d121bd3cd6600ff2cd8594a","tid":21